items.postText: Richard A: "I hope CDG's Robert Kennedy impersonation doesn't last. He used to bowl single overs that were the length of a decent spell. He bowled so many wides, he used to have to stay on the field during the lunch break just to finish his overs." --- That's 46-year-old ex NZ cricketer Robert Kennedy he's referring to
